{"type":"answer","id":269557,"parentType":"question","parentId":25650,"uid":2296,"contents":"<blockquote>Quinine can cause serious side effects on your heart, kidneys, or blood cells. Stop taking this medicine and call your doctor immediately if you have the following symptoms:<br>\n<br>\n<ul><li>Headache with chest pain and severe dizziness</li><li>Fast or pounding heartbeats</li><li>Unusual bruising or bleeding (nosebleeds, bleeding gums, purple or red spots under your skin) signs of infection (fever, chills, mouth sores)</li><li>Severe lower back pain</li><li>Blood in your urine</li></ul><br>\n</blockquote><br>\n不当使用奎宁会造成心率不齐和心梗，本来就是处方药，川普说要用奎宁预防新冠，没感染就吃完全没用而且对于中老年来说，心率不齐和心梗是致命的，有人去模仿的话后果非常严重，本来奎宁用药就是医生的权力，现在鼓励民众拿奎宁当板蓝根来用。这和习近平推广中药有什么区别？<br>\n<br>\n<blockquote>羟氯喹心脏毒性表现为快速发展的双心室心肌病<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamanetworkopen/fullarticle/2765499?utm_source=For_The_Media&amp;amp%3butm_medium=referral&amp;amp%3butm_campaign=ftm_links&amp;amp%3butm_term=042420\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamanetworkopen/fullarticle/2765499?utm_source=For_The_Media&amp;amp%3butm_medium=referral&amp;amp%3butm_campaign=ftm_links&amp;amp%3butm_term=042420</a></blockquote><br>\n奎宁实验组里面已经有两人死于心脏病。<br>\n<br>\n<blockquote>On the other hand, there is much we are still learning about COVID-19 infection. There are many patients with a direct myocardial effect from the virus. It is possible that the virus has a direct membrane effect leading to rhythm instability. There are some patients who develop a myocarditis that can range from subclinical to fulminant. These patients are likely to be at higher risk for ventricular arrhythmias as well. There are still other patients who develop vascular abnormalities and thrombosis which could lead to myocardial ischemia and a propensity towards ventricular arrhythmias. The science on this is evolving quickly and is not fully established at this point.</blockquote><br>\n这位医生的观点，武汉肺炎有可能会导致心肌炎和心率不齐，这可能会放大奎宁的副作用。所以奎宁的治疗需要继续研究。<br>\n<br>\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/untrusted fake 2049bbsnt/10.1101/2020.04.07.20056424v2<br />\nChloroquine diphosphate in two different dosages as adjunctive therapy of hospitalized patients with severe respiratory syndrome in the context of coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2) infection: Preliminary safety results of a randomized, double-blinded, phase IIb clinical trial (CloroCovid-19 Study)<br />\n<br />\n</a></blockquote><br />\n这篇研究显示了两者均用于治疗疟疾的氯喹和羟氯喹对某些患者可能造成重大伤害，特别是致命性心律失常的风险。试验中的患者还接受了抗生素阿奇霉素，后者具有相同的心脏病风险。美国的医院也使用阿奇霉素治疗冠状病毒患者，通常与羟氯喹联用。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>“To me, this study conveys one useful piece of information, which is that chloroquine causes a dose-dependent increase in an abnormality in the ECG that could predispose people to sudden cardiac death,” said Dr. David Juurlink, an internist and the head of the division of clinical pharmacology at the University of Toronto, referring to an electrocardiogram, which reads the heart’s electrical activity.</blockquote><br />\n多伦多大学的专家也表示潜在的心源性心房颤动和心率不齐和奎宁有关。<br />\n<blockquote>The FDA does not allow the use of the drug for the prevention of Covid-19, and The American Medical Association, American Pharmacists Association and American Society of Health-System Pharmacists&nbsp;<b>have issued a joint statement opposing the use of hydroxychloroquine for the prevention of Covid-19.</b></blockquote><br />\nFDA，美国医疗协会，美国药剂师协会，美国社会医疗体系协会联名反对使用奎宁为预防武汉肺炎的药物。真当自己伟大领袖，一句话顶一万句了？\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n\n</a><div class=\"meta clearfix\"><a href=\"https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/untrusted fake 2049bbsnt/10.1101/2020.04.07.20056424v2<br />\nChloroquine diphosphate in two different dosages as adjunctive therapy of hospitalized patients with severe respiratory syndrome in the context of coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2) infection: Preliminary safety results of a randomized, double-blinded, phase IIb clinical trial (CloroCovid-19 Study)<br />\n<br />\n</a></blockquote><br />\n这篇研究显示了两者均用于治疗疟疾的氯喹和羟氯喹对某些患者可能造成重大伤害，特别是致命性心律失常的风险。试验中的患者还接受了抗生素阿奇霉素，后者具有相同的心脏病风险。美国的医院也使用阿奇霉素治疗冠状病毒患者，通常与羟氯喹联用。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>“To me, this study conveys one useful piece of information, which is that chloroquine causes a dose-dependent increase in an abnormality in the ECG that could predispose people to sudden cardiac death,” said Dr. David Juurlink, an internist and the head of the division of clinical pharmacology at the University of Toronto, referring to an electrocardiogram, which reads the heart’s electrical activity.</blockquote><br />\n多伦多大学的专家也表示潜在的心源性心房颤动和心率不齐和奎宁有关。<br />\n<blockquote>The FDA does not allow the use of the drug for the prevention of Covid-19, and The American Medical Association, American Pharmacists Association and American Society of Health-System Pharmacists&nbsp;<b>have issued a joint statement opposing the use of hydroxychloroquine for the prevention of Covid-19.</b></blockquote><br />\nFDA，美国医疗协会，美国药剂师协会，美国社会医疗体系协会联名反对使用奎宁为预防武汉肺炎的药物。真当自己伟大领袖，一句话顶一万句了？\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"aw-small-text pull-right\">2020-05-20</span>\n\n<span class=\"operate aw-vote-ui\">\n</span></a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree disabled\">\n<i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">2</b>\n</a>\n\n\n<span class=\"operate\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"toggle_disscusion($(this));\" class=\"aw-add-comment\" data-id=\"269557\" data-type=\"answer\" data-comment-count=\"4\"><i class=\"icon icon-comment\"></i> 4</a>\n </span>\n\n<div class=\"more-operate\">\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-answer__item_id-269557\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"icon icon-users\"></i></a>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box\" style=\"display:none\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-list\"></div>\n\n<a class=\"aw-load-more-content\">\n<span>更多</span>\n</a>\n\n<form action=\"/question/ajax/save_answer_discussion/answer_id-269557\" method=\"post\" onsubmit=\"return false\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box-main\">\n<textarea class=\"aw-comment-txt autosize form-control\" rows=\"2\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"讨论一下...\"></textarea>\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box-btn\">\n<span class=\"pull-right\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"btn btn-mini btn-success\" onclick=\"submit_disscusion($(this));\">讨论</a>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n\n</blockquote>","date":"2020-05-20","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":4}